<placeName cert="high">Philadelphia</placeName></head><div lang="grc" part="N" type="edition"><ab part="N">
    <lb n="1"/>Ζήνωνι χαίρειν 

    <lb n="2"/>Ἑρμίας. γίνωσκε ὅτι 

    <lb n="3"/>ἥκει ὁ ἀδελφὸς 

    <lb n="4"/>ἐπ᾽ ἐμέ, καλῶν με εἰς 

    <lb n="5"/><choice><corr>Μέμφιν</corr><sic>μενφιν</sic></choice>· ὁ γὰρ Ἀγαθοκλῆς 

    <lb n="6"/><choice><corr>ἐν</corr><sic>εμ</sic></choice> <choice><corr>Μέμφει</corr><sic>μενφει</sic></choice> ἐστὶν καὶ ἀνα-

    <lb n="7"/>πλεῖ εἰς τὴν Θηβαίδα. 

    <lb n="8"/>σὺ οὖν, εἴ σοι δοκεῖ, περὶ ὧν 

    <lb n="9"/>σοι πρότερον συνελά-

    <lb n="10"/>λησα, ὡς τοῦ ἀνθρώπου 

    <lb n="11"/>χρείαν ἔχοντος κερμα-

    <lb n="12"/>τίου, σὺ οὖν περί μου 

    <lb n="13"/>γράψον πρὸς αὐτόν, 

    <lb n="14"/>ὅπως ἂν φιλανθρωπήσηι 

    <lb n="15"/>τὰ πρὸς ἡμᾶς καὶ τὸ τάχος 

    <lb n="16"/>ἀποστείληι με. ἐὰν οὖν 

    <lb n="17"/>εἰδῶ τὰ περὶ ἐμὲ εν τίνι 

    <lb n="18"/>εἰμί, ἵνα καὶ <choice><corr>τὴν</corr><sic>τημ</sic></choice> μητέρα 

    <lb n="19"/>καὶ τὸ ἀδέλφιον μετα-

    <lb n="20"/>πέμψωμαι ὧδε. 

    <lb n="21"/>εὐτύχει. </ab></div><div n="meta.1068" part="N" type="description"><p><rs cert="high" type="material">Papyrus</rs></p></div><div n="meta.1068" part="N" subtype="textDate" type="commentary"><p><date notAfter="-226" notBefore="-275" type="textDate">Mitte III v.Chr.</date></p></div><div n="meta.1068" part="N" subtype="general" type="commentary"><p>Datierung nach dem Rahmen des Zenon - Archivs.</p></div><div n="meta.1068" part="N" subtype="principalEdition" type="bibliography"><listBibl><bibl subtype="principal" type="publication"><title level="s" type="abbreviated">P.Cair. Zen.</title><biblScope type="volume">3</biblScope><biblScope type="numbers">59428</biblScope></bibl><bibl type="Trismegistos"><biblScope type="numbers">1068</biblScope></bibl><bibl type="DDbDP"><series>0092</series>; <biblScope type="volume">3</biblScope>; <biblScope type="numbers">59428</biblScope></bibl></listBibl><p>Perseus links: <xref evaluate="all" from="ROOT" href="0092;3;59428" targOrder="Y" to="DITTO" type="Perseus">Text in Perseus</xref></p></div><div n="meta.1068" part="N" subtype="illustrations" type="bibliography"><p>keine</p></div><div n="meta.1068" part="N" subtype="locations" type="history"><p><placeName cert="low" type="ancientFindspot">Philadelphia (Arsinoites)</placeName></p></div><div n="meta.1068" part="N" type="figure"><p><figure href="http://ipap.csad.ox.ac.uk/4DLink4/4DACTION/IPAPwebquery?vPub=P.Cair.Zen.&amp;vVol=3&amp;vNum=59428"><figDesc>Abbildung im Internet</figDesc></figure></p></div></body></text></TEI.2>